BakeIntervalInSeconds: The interval between baked keys when there is no valid Display Rate and Tick Resolution.
bCustomRangeOverride: When enabled, CustomRange will be used for the bake region. Otherwise the selected keys will be used.
CustomRangeMinInSeconds: Specifies a custom range to use for baking when there is no valid Display Rate and Tick Resolution.
CustomRangeMaxInSeconds: Specifies a custom range to use for baking when there is no valid Display Rate and Tick Resolution.
CustomRange: Specifies a custom range to use for baking
